From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Tue, 29 Apr 2025 17:41:24 -0700
Subject: perf symbol-elf: Integrate rust-v0 demangling
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e20848c317b51e74953c38cd14ab2926baa1608b
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Use the demangle-rust-v0 APIs to see if symbol is Rust mangled and
demangle if so.

The API requires a pre-allocated output buffer, some estimation and
retrying are added for this.

